Author: feelingpensive
Text: Ugh I literally feel like a huge chunky gorl at all times and just want to complain about it but I know people will think I’m just fishing for compliments or being dumb if I do  It’s hard to explain to people like I genuinely see myself as larger than I am

Author: gayshitlord
Text: I can relate so hard to this shit. My boss’s dad said that he doesn’t think that I eat after work. I don’t see thinness either. All I can see is my spare tire.
